These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, rock, jazz, salsa, reggae, trance, pop
1. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
4. the fan of reggae is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of jazz##2
5. the fan of salsa is between the fan of rock and the fan of hip-hop##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | pop | jazz | reggae | hip-hop | salsa | rock | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, hiking, card-games, writing, rock-climbing, reading, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | reading | magic-tricks | board-games | card-games | writing | hiking | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: photography, dancing, singing, collecting, chess, puzzles, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | drawing | puzzles | chess | dancing | photography | singing | collecting |

